WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.084 --> 00:00:02.521
The school budget.
which Anderson single-handedly oversees.

2
00:00:02.545 --> 00:00:04.940
said we spent $129 on mousepads.

3
00:00:04.964 --> 00:00:06.358
No mousepads.

4
00:00:06.382 --> 00:00:07.984
You know how I feel about protecting Liz.

5
00:00:08.008 --> 00:00:09.236
I apologized.

6
00:00:09.260 --> 00:00:10.529
Previously on Elle...

7
00:00:10.553 --> 00:00:12.155
Robin's funeral
will be in Denver.

8
00:00:12.179 --> 00:00:14.491
where most of her family lives.
so I panicked

9
00:00:14.515 --> 00:00:16.535
and offered to throw her a memorial.

10
00:00:16.559 --> 00:00:17.661
Let me help.

11
00:00:17.685 --> 00:00:20.497
Whoever Robin was to you...

12
00:00:20.521 --> 00:00:23.357
thank you for being here today
to pay your respects.

13
00:00:24.567 --> 00:00:25.877
I'm so sorry for your loss.

14
00:00:25.901 --> 00:00:27.587
I appreciate that.

15
00:00:27.611 --> 00:00:29.631
-I kissed Elle.
-I don't want to look at you!

16
00:00:29.655 --> 00:00:33.385
I don't want to be around you. and you can
tell Elle I am done with her. too!

17
00:00:33.409 --> 00:00:35.619
I don't want to lose Shannon as a friend.

18
00:00:52.928 --> 00:00:54.221
These are for you.

19
00:00:55.639 --> 00:00:58.201
And these are for your daughter.

20
00:00:58.225 --> 00:01:01.103
who's probably never
going to speak to me again.

21
00:01:02.563 --> 00:01:06.376
I am so. so sorry.

22
00:01:06.400 --> 00:01:08.194
To both of you.

23
00:01:12.406 --> 00:01:14.092
You know. while I have you here.

24
00:01:14.116 --> 00:01:16.261
maybe you could put in
a good word to Shannon.

25
00:01:16.285 --> 00:01:18.096
She's gone. too.

26
00:01:18.120 --> 00:01:20.223
Well. she's not dead. obviously.

27
00:01:20.247 --> 00:01:21.927
Not that there's anything wrong with that.

28
00:01:24.084 --> 00:01:28.482
I'm so sorry I... I kissed Miles.

29
00:01:28.506 --> 00:01:31.443
Your daughter had recently
broken up with him.

30
00:01:31.467 --> 00:01:33.945
She broke up with him.

31
00:01:33.969 --> 00:01:38.349
I don't know if you caught that
before you... you know.

32
00:01:40.059 --> 00:01:41.977
But I will make this right.

33
00:01:43.646 --> 00:01:46.374
Hey!

34
00:01:46.398 --> 00:01:49.902
Some of us are busy
paying our respects here.

35
00:01:53.239 --> 00:01:56.408
Why isn't there a stop sign
at this intersection?

36
00:01:57.910 --> 00:02:00.287
Why isn't there a stop sign
at this intersection?

37
00:02:12.550 --> 00:02:14.110
One will suffice.

38
00:02:14.134 --> 00:02:16.822
Hi. I have this petition for a stop sign.

39
00:02:16.846 --> 00:02:20.200
There's this really dangerous intersection
near our school.

40
00:02:20.224 --> 00:02:22.685
You'll see
I have the requisite 1.000 signatures.

41
00:02:24.603 --> 00:02:28.416
So. you're going to win Shannon back
with a stop sign?

42
00:02:28.440 --> 00:02:31.253
Seems like it would've been easier
to just not kiss her boyfriend.

43
00:02:31.277 --> 00:02:35.006
Ex-boyfriend. She means ex-boyfriend.

44
00:02:35.030 --> 00:02:38.844
That detail's not
for public consumption yet.

45
00:02:38.868 --> 00:02:41.662
And this isn't about Shannon and me.
It's for the greater good.

46
00:02:43.163 --> 00:02:47.686
I can't undo the mistake I made.
but this is something I can do.

47
00:02:47.710 --> 00:02:49.354
With your help. of course.

48
00:02:49.378 --> 00:02:50.730
According to our records.

49
00:02:50.754 --> 00:02:55.068
we already approved a stop sign
at the corner of 50th and Evans.

50
00:02:55.092 --> 00:02:57.112
Last June. in fact.

51
00:02:57.136 --> 00:03:01.074
I can assure you. there is
no such stop sign at said intersection.

52
00:03:01.098 --> 00:03:03.159
We approved the stop sign.

53
00:03:03.183 --> 00:03:06.312
but the school elected
to handle contracting themselves.

54
00:03:07.646 --> 00:03:09.666
Sorry. I-I don't understand.

55
00:03:09.690 --> 00:03:13.587
Are you saying someone ordered a stop sign
but never paid for it?

56
00:03:13.611 --> 00:03:15.797
It says right here.

57
00:03:15.821 --> 00:03:17.257
"One stop sign.

58
00:03:17.281 --> 00:03:21.177
requested by and granted
to Rainier West High School board.

59
00:03:21.201 --> 00:03:23.954
point of contact Shane Anderson."

