And they don't have kids.

766
00:42:55.448 --> 00:42:56.801
I've seen that jacket before.

767
00:42:56.825 --> 00:42:59.095
I knew
it didn't belong to his wife.

768
00:42:59.119 --> 00:43:01.097
He was dismissed from a school
in Sunnyside. Washington.

769
00:43:01.121 --> 00:43:02.306
for unknown reasons.

770
00:43:02.330 --> 00:43:04.684
This girl's wearing a shirt
that says Sunnyside.

771
00:43:04.708 --> 00:43:06.835
Seems like she's the unknown reason.

772
00:43:08.086 --> 00:43:10.964
So. we're saying this girl
is his daughter?

773
00:43:11.756 --> 00:43:13.567
Wow.

774
00:43:13.591 --> 00:43:16.362
I mean. I thought he was having an affair.

775
00:43:16.386 --> 00:43:19.657
but I never thought
he'd have a whole secret family.

776
00:43:19.681 --> 00:43:22.410
Maybe he was stealing the money
to provide for them.

777
00:43:22.434 --> 00:43:25.454
Yeah. but that still doesn't explain
the note.

778
00:43:25.478 --> 00:43:27.206
Unless the money
isn't for his family.

779
00:43:27.230 --> 00:43:28.499
It's a pretty big secret.

780
00:43:28.523 --> 00:43:30.683
Almost worth stealing
thousands of dollars to cover up.

781
00:43:32.485 --> 00:43:35.423
He was paying someone to keep quiet.

782
00:43:35.447 --> 00:43:36.948
Someone must be blackmailing him.

783
00:43:42.912 --> 00:43:43.973
Guys. I need your help.

784
00:43:43.997 --> 00:43:45.999
It's my mom.

785
00:43:51.338 --> 00:43:52.922
Oh. fuck.

786
00:43:59.721 --> 00:44:01.073
What do they want with your mom?

787
00:44:01.097 --> 00:44:03.284
-She swears she didn't do anything.
-Why were they there?

788
00:44:03.308 --> 00:44:05.328
This is the police!

789
00:44:05.352 --> 00:44:08.581
Step out of your car with your hands up.

790
00:44:08.605 --> 00:44:09.790
They were there to arrest her.

791
00:44:09.814 --> 00:44:11.584
-Okay.
-Look. thousands of dollars in cash

792
00:44:11.608 --> 00:44:13.085
was reported stolen from school today.

793
00:44:13.109 --> 00:44:14.253
We got the items.

794
00:44:14.277 --> 00:44:16.905
Look. "Rainier West High."
written all over them.

795
00:44:19.407 --> 00:44:20.658
Those aren't mine.

796
00:44:23.078 --> 00:44:24.537
They found it in her car.

797
00:44:25.455 --> 00:44:28.291
What? That's impossible.
Donna would never steal.

798
00:44:30.627 --> 00:44:32.104
Well. she'd never steal that much.

799
00:44:32.128 --> 00:44:33.606
That doesn't make any sense.

800
00:44:33.630 --> 00:44:35.524
Donna wasn't even at the school today.

801
00:44:35.548 --> 00:44:37.401
Yes. she was. You remember? She...

802
00:44:37.425 --> 00:44:39.945
she dropped off my lunch.

803
00:44:39.969 --> 00:44:43.866
Okay. but Donna was the one
who told us about the receipts.

804
00:44:43.890 --> 00:44:45.368
And then tried to convince us
not to look for them.

805
00:44:45.392 --> 00:44:46.744
Didn't we just realize
that someone

806
00:44:46.768 --> 00:44:48.770
was blackmailing Anderson?

807
00:44:50.063 --> 00:44:52.124
I'm sorry. what are you talking about?

808
00:44:52.148 --> 00:44:56.152
We think Anderson has a secret family
and someone knows about it.

809
00:44:57.237 --> 00:44:58.696
What?

810
00:45:00.073 --> 00:45:01.467
And you think my mom is blackmailing him?

811
00:45:01.491 --> 00:45:03.010
No. No way.

812
00:45:03.034 --> 00:45:04.619
Donna couldn't have done this.

813
00:45:11.543 --> 00:45:13.211
Could she?

814
00:45:16.756 --> 00:45:20.236
♪ I say la. la-la-la-la ♪

815
00:45:20.260 --> 00:45:22.613
♪ la-la-la-la ♪

816
00:45:22.637 --> 00:45:26.575
♪ la-la-la-la-la-la-la-la-la-la ♪

817
00:45:26.599 --> 00:45:30.830
♪ la-la-la-la. la-la-la-la ♪

818
00:45:30.854 --> 00:45:35.251
♪ la-la-la-la-la-la-la-la-la-la ♪

819
00:45:35.275 --> 00:45:39.463
♪ la-la-la-la. la-la-la-la ♪

820
00:45:39.487 --> 00:45:43.175
♪ la-la-la-la-la-la-la-la-la-la ♪

821
00:45:43.199 --> 00:45:46.035
♪ When you walk on by ♪

822
00:45:47.620 --> 00:45:52.017
♪ will you call my name? ♪

823
